data.name: label7.Text
data.value: Supported commands : MOV : Move from current location to specified location(Ex : MOV P1). DLY : Delay miliseconds (Ex: DLY 1000). SPD : Set speed for robot (Ex: SPD 1000). MVS : Similar to the mov command, but it will wait for the execution of all previous statements before executing this command (Ex: MVS P1). MOUT : Digital output (Ex : MOUT 0 1 ==== 0 is number of output and 1 is value of output). WAIT MIN I J :Wait Input I = J (Ex:WAIT MIN 0 1 : WAIT INPUT 0 = TRUE).
